{"tid":737671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 無錫一高校被曝強迫學生搬到舊宿舍 把好宿舍留給留學生 引發學生抗爭","createTime":"2018-07-11T04:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T04:18:29.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1d929f92c4c231adf5e54da3ee85799939a13726","tid":737671,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"無錫職業技術學院遭學生曝光強迫學生搬宿舍。該同學稱學校領導讓大二學生搬進條件較差的宿舍樓住，把好宿舍留給留學生，且「原先是6人一間的宿舍，到留學生手裡就變成了2-3人一間」。據稱，9日晚，前來催促搬遷的老師代表在遭到學生拒絕後，情緒失控，還對學生進行了暴力威脅。目前，該同學曝光此事的微博已全被刪除，原因不明。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ww4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006qEEUFly1ft5ile3sm0j30c80lmtcg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006qEEUFly1ft5ile3sm0j30c80lmtcg.jpg&h=011f8b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j7QrXlrlbPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj7QrXlrlbPU&d=gvI0%2BlcAl1%2BK8K%2Bnf0wR73Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=532a9d33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j7QrXlrlbPU</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.weibo.com/5890672121/4260491004018309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.weibo.com%2F5890672121%2F4260491004018309&d=gvI0%2BlcAl1%2BK8K%2Bnf0wR73Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a8ed8545\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.weibo.com/5890672121/4260491004018309</a>"},{"pid":"8eb95a12cccdd88be477342955fe6cefea0345af","tid":737671,"uid":90392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:15:47.000Z","msg":"厲害了, 共的國"},{"pid":"b63bb82cb7a351ca789fd52b96d46995984555f7","tid":737671,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:16:51.000Z","msg":"有咩人去支那留學?"},{"pid":"9c7683c0ce2a5184f851a8b784f2a3ca56c854e7","tid":737671,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b63bb82cb7a351ca789fd52b96d46995984555f7","tid":737671,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T0